Package: prepim
Type: Package
Title: Prepare Input Data for PIM
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: person("Graham", "Parsons", email = "graham.parsons@ons.gov.uk",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Carries out the preparation steps on the input datasets required
  for the Perpetual Inventory Method, including aggregating and consolidating
  GFCF time series, standarising coding schemes and joining historic to
  contemporary data.
License: file LICENCE
Depends:
  futile.logger
Imports:
  assertr,
  dplyr,
  readr,
  readxl,
  tidyr,
  zoo,
  pimIO
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests: testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
